### ─── Home (Public) ───

### Home landing data
GET {{baseUrl}}/home

### ─── Anime (Public) ───

### Catalog
GET {{baseUrl}}/anime

### Catalog with search
GET {{baseUrl}}/anime?q=naruto&page=1&pageSize=10

### Catalog with filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/anime?genre=Action&status=ONGOING&type=TV&sort=recent

### Catalog sorted by most viewed
GET {{baseUrl}}/anime?sort=most_viewed&page=1&pageSize=24

### Anime by slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/anime/naruto

### ─── Episodes for Upload (UPLOADER, ADMIN) ───

### List episodes with upload status (paginated, 50 per page)
GET {{baseUrl}}/anime/naruto/episodes?page=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### List episodes page 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/anime/naruto/episodes?page=2&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### List episodes page 3 (for long anime like One Piece)
GET {{baseUrl}}/anime/one-piece/episodes?page=1&pageSize=100
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ─── Episode detail (Public) ───

### Episode by slug and number
GET {{baseUrl}}/anime/naruto/episodes/2
